data.title: Liberty North High School
data.text:
Liberty North High School Class of 2024 Graduate Trey Snyder was drafted to play Major League Baseball on Tuesday, July 15, 2024.

Trey Snyder of Liberty North High School is the 2023-24 Gatorade Missouri Baseball Player of the Year. Snyder is the second Gatorade Missouri Baseball Player of the Year to be chosen from Liberty North High School.

The Returning Student Registration portal for the 2024-2025 school year is now open! If your student is currently enrolled in Liberty Public Schools, you need to complete the Returning Student Registration for your student.

The Northland Regional Chamber of Commerce hosted its annual Excellence in Education banquet on Wednesday night, May 1, 2024, and six LPS employees were recognized with honors.

Liberty Public Schools will host its annual Retiring Staff Reception and Program on Wednesday, May 8, 2024. It will be held from 4:30-6 p.m. at the Liberty High School Performing Arts Center.
